      "content": "credit counselors and advisors... they just want to talk about more ways to manage the pain, but the pain is the same. it's just the crushing reality of it. i look at my bank account and then i look at the interest rates and it feels like a trap that's already closed. maybe there's just no \"small step\" that actually fixes a hole this deep. it feels like a permanent problem.",
